= Textile Toolbar Extension for Radiant

Adds toolbars to Textile-enabled text areas in the admin.

== Installation

From the target Radiant project:
  
  git clone git://github.com/pelargir/radiant-textile-toolbar-extension.git vendor/extensions/textile-toolbar

Start your project, login as an admin, and visit the Extensions page. The Textile
Toolbar extension should be listed there.

